\c 29
\s Izwi raJehovha
\p
\v 1 Ipai, Jehovha, imi vanakomana vaMwari, Ipai Jehovha kudzo nesimba.
\v 2 Ipai Jehovha kudzo yakafanirwa
\s nezita rake;
\s Namatai kuna Jehovha nenguo tsvene.
\s zwi ralehovha riri pamusoro pemvura zhinji;
\s Mwari wokubwinya unotinhira,
\s Iye Jehovha ari pamusoro pemvura zhinji-zhinji,
\p
\v 4 Izwi raJehovha rine simba;
\s Izwi raJehovha rizere noumambo.
\p
\v 5 Izwi raJehovha rinovhuna misidhari; Zvirokwazvo, Jehovha
\s anovhunanya misidhari yeRebhanoni.
\p
\v 6 Anoipemberesa semhuru;
\s Iro Rebhanoni neSirioni semhuru yenyati.
\p
\v 7 Izwi raJehovha rinopamura
\s mirazvo yomoto.
\p
\v 8 Izwi raJehovha rinodederesa renje; Jehovha anodederesa renje reKadheshi.
\p
\v 9 Izwi raJehovha rinoberekesa nondo, Rinosvuura miti yamatondo; Nomutemberi yake zvose zvinoti, "Kubwinya."
\p
\v 10 Jehovha akagara pachigaro
\s chohushe
\s paboporodzi remvura;
\s Zvirokwazvo, Jehovha anogara ari mambo nokusingaperi.
\p
\v 11 Jehovha achapa vanhu vake simba; Jehovha acharopafadza vanhu vake norugare.
